{"tid":2217013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：官方宣傳片回顧一年大事  台慶祝雙十節 毋忘撐港（李八方）","createTime":"2020-09-25T06:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T12:18:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb926e9e6d4a6cbdd61e3259e9bf598f4a250a07","tid":2217013,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/5KGEBOBSSNG2VLOSBODK3DYPYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2F5KGEBOBSSNG2VLOSBODK3DYPYU%2F&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwztVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=358cf36f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200925%2F5KGEBOBSSNG2VLOSBODK3DYPYU%2F&h=e69b7415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200925/5KGEBOBSSNG2VLOSBODK3DYPYU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：官方宣傳片回顧一年大事 <br />\n台慶祝雙十節 毋忘撐港（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-tlFyk_z7t1-WX_ei5Coz-bYYGg=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WULAMFTJ4JC6RCQINRJYFAEMLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-tlFyk_z7t1-WX_ei5Coz-bYYGg%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWULAMFTJ4JC6RCQINRJYFAEMLY.jpg&h=ae14a956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■外交部影片包括蔡英文同林榮基見面一幕。<br />\n<br />\n雙十台灣國慶就到，外交部噚日就發佈一條「攜手同心、台灣前進」國慶影片，當中包含好多過去一年台灣大事，包括口罩外交「Taiwan can help」，後半部份仲有唔少香港相關畫面，強調堅持民主自由嘅價值，睇嚟台灣堅決向北京說不嘅態度都相當明確嘞。<br />\n<br />\n國慶影片嘅內容前半部份主要講台灣同國際合作，包括武漢肺炎時送贈物資畀外國嘅「Taiwan can help」活動，更加插好多外國元首表示感謝嘅畫面。。。。。。。。。。。。影片又加入捷克參議院議長到訪台灣講「我是台灣人」嘅畫面，令人不禁諗起布拉格同北京解除姊妹市關係，不知不覺間台灣今年喺國際多咗唔少朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e0NlrwfrsyO1DRp0dbXfnB8Qnwg=/1571x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PPVAWH4KBFBHNFBZDJOXWQLQIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe0NlrwfrsyO1DRp0dbXfnB8Qnwg%3D%2F1571x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPPVAWH4KBFBHNFBZDJOXWQLQIY.jpg&h=4a3da5b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■影片又播出台灣撐港遊行畫面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ClYN-L9Y0MWaN3bGyjHeSxHqG0s=/1571x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PVTBUT6DQBHLHIFA33NEJ7E4FM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FClYN-L9Y0MWaN3bGyjHeSxHqG0s%3D%2F1571x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPVTBUT6DQBHLHIFA33NEJ7E4FM.jpg&h=888672fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■自由廣場集會，撐住香港的自由。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重溫小英到訪銅鑼灣書店<br />\n<br />\n影片中段以「民主典範 全球支持」為題，講總統選舉之餘，仲播放台灣銅鑼灣書店片段，見到蔡英文同曾被中共擄走嘅銅鑼灣書店店長林榮基見面，畫面聚焦當日蔡英文送贈書店嘅親筆感言：「自由的台灣撐住香港的自由」。仲有外交部部長吳釗燮到訪銅鑼灣書店，又影住《獅子山下》歌詞「我哋大家用艱辛努力寫下那不朽香江名句」，背景仲有「光復香港，時代革命」㖭。隨後更加有台灣撐港示威畫面，同埋今年成立幫助港人嘅台港服務交流辦公室，撐港撐到咁出面，實在唔話得！<br />\n<br />\n八方發現影片雖然冇乜點提過中國，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"6b26725205b5f624162d1cb1600309ffe3191b82","tid":2217013,"uid":227813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">用過Condom點會再用呢？</span></strong></span>"}]}